2. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper uses clustering and log-likelihood ratio tests to combine evidence of local cues. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper uses deep networks and voting methods to detect semantic parts. 
4. cs.CL (Computation and Language) is less likely but still possible as the paper deals with semantic understanding of objects. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also less likely but possible as the paper deals with visual cues and images.
